parameters:
Weapon Shop's Father: "Don't you dare touch my
daughter aaaaaah!!"

Ruth: "Heh heh heh, looks like the old man isn't
around."

Ruth: "And here, there's only this girl... Well,
there's only one thing to do then."

Weapon Shop's Daughter: "Eek... no... don't
come... please..."

Ruth: "Huh, even someone like me can scare
someone... Interesting."

Ruth: "This could turn out to be quite
entertaining."

Noah: "Lord Ruth... please command me as you
wish♥"

Ruth: "Hmm, she's already brainwashed... but how
should I use her..."

Ruth: "Looking around, it seems like a weapon
shop... Unfortunately, I can't really use weapons
properly."

Ruth: "Was this a waste of time... Oh! That's
right!"

Ruth: "You, bring your father back and hold him
off. It's better for me if there are fewer people
looking for me!"

Noah: "Yes, Lord Ruth. I will hold him back so he
won't disturb you, please rest assured."

I left the house and quickly moved away from the
place.

Ruth: "Noah should have brought her father back by
now, hopefully this will make it easier for me to
move around..."
Ruth: "You stay put and behave yourself here."

Weapons Shop Owner: "Wha-, a monster has
infiltrated the village!?"

Weapons Shop Owner: "I'll go and slay it right
now!"
Ruth: (Damn, this is bad... I have to escape...!)

Weapons Shop Owner: "Wha- A monster's gotten into
the village!?"

Weapons Shop Owner: "I'll go and slay it right
now!"
Weapon Shop Owner: "I've caught you! Give it up!"
